_:Nddffbc28f25143ad944681302aad9046 <http://schema.org/description> "The Northern Ireland Executive is the administrative branch of the Northern Ireland Assembly, the devolved legislature for Northern Ireland. It is responsible for matters including enterprise, trade and investment, agriculture and rural development, education, health, policing and justice, environment and regional development. Northern Ireland Executive is a devolved government, supported by 10 agencies and public bodies ." .
